

        There is an  Existing Form and When you enter the Data                                      
               and On Submit Need To Open Pop-Up(Dialog) 
               
     ==========================================================================================          


<!-- Form Pop up -->
     <div id="popup-modal" style="display:none;">
         <span><?= $block->escapeHtml(__('Business Name')) ?></span>
          <p id="bn"> </p>

